          h3.spacer Clean, Concise
          p Iâ€™m a major proponent of code readability and organization. It's not just about whether a product functions properly or not. No one wants to be refactoring a mountain of technical debt before building a new feature. Readable, modular code leads to easier maintainability and fewer bugs. Which in the end, is just as important as meeting a deadline.

