  #designer
    .section-header-container
      h2 User Interface Engineer
      p I'm a design-minded engineer passionate about implementing the experience of a design in it's best possible form.
    .section-container.row
      .col-sm-3.column.collapse-left
        h3 Don't Just Tell, Show
        p There's a difference between neatly displaying information and telling a story. Design elements should come together to create an experience that not only gets the message across but also captures the essence of the product or brand.
        a.button.designer-button-behance(href='http://codepen.io/alecortega/' target='blank')
          i.fa.fa-codepen.fa-lg
          | &nbsp; VIEW CODEPEN
        h3 All Things Considered
        p There's more that goes into design than just making it look pretty. Things like client constraints and use cases need to be taken into consideration. Anyone can make something look nice, it's about making it feel natural and familiar to use.
      .center-column.col-sm-6.hidden-xs
        #browser-designer-trigger
          img.browser#browser-designer-element(src='http://res.cloudinary.com/alecoortega/image/upload/c_scale,q_80,w_1100/v1438045377/BrowserHiFi_bocbwq.jpg' alt='High Fidelity Browser Mockup')

      .col-sm-3.column.collapse-right
        h3.spacer-medium-down Software
        ul
          li
            i.devicon-photoshop-plain
            span Photoshop
          li
            i.devicon-illustrator-plain
            span Illustrator
          li
            i.fa.fa-diamond
            span Sketch 3
          li
            i.fa.fa-bars
            span Framer.js
          li
            i.devicon-trello-plain
            span Trello

        h3.spacer Design for Empathy
        p The technology used to product a product is easily forgotten, but the feeling you envoke in a user is what lasts. Designs should always be created with the user's perspective and the overall experience in mind. An empathetic experience is far more powerful than any colored call-to-action button.


